## Architecture

Follow **Clean Architecture + MVVM**:

- **Model layer**: `lib/data/models/trip/` — pure data classes with `fromJson` / `toJson`
- **Service layer**: `lib/data/services/trip/` — HTTP calls, return `Result<T>`
- **ViewModel layer**: `lib/ui/user/trip/*/view_models/` — `ChangeNotifier` with state
- **Screen layer**: `lib/ui/user/trip/*/` — UI widgets, use `Consumer<>` or `context.watch`

## State Management

- All ViewModels extend `ChangeNotifier`
- ViewModels receive services via constructor: `TripService`, `TripBookingRepository`
- Screens receive ViewModels via `context.read<T>()` from Provider tree
- Register all Trip ViewModels in `lib/config/dependencies.dart`

## API Integration

Use OpenAPI endpoints from `coach-trip-controller` and `coach-booking-controller`:

| Action | Method | Endpoint |
|--------|--------|----------|
| Search trips | POST | `/api/v1/coach-trips/search` |
| Get seats | GET | `/api/v1/coach-trips/{tripId}/seats` |
| Create booking | POST | `/api/v1/coach-bookings` |
| Get booking | GET | `/api/v1/coach-bookings/{bookingId}` |
| Cancel booking | POST | `/api/v1/coach-bookings/{bookingId}/cancel` |
| Create payment | POST | `/api/v1/coach-bookings/{bookingId}/payment` |
| Get stations | GET | `/api/v1/stations` |
| List my bookings | GET | `/api/v1/coach-bookings` |

## Booking Flow

1. `TripHomeScreen` → pick origin/destination/date
2. `TripListScreen` → browse results with filters
3. `SeatPickerScreen` → select seats (single or double-decker)
4. `TripBookingInputScreen` → enter contact info
5. `TripBookingReviewScreen` → review and confirm
6. `TripPaymentScreen` → VNPay WebView
7. `TripPaymentResultScreen` → success/failure

## Cancellation Flow

1. `MyTripBookingScreen` → list bookings with NavigationRail
2. `TripBookingDetailScreen` → booking details
3. `TripCancelScreen` → confirm cancellation
4. `TripCancelSuccessScreen` → cancellation result

## Code Quality

- **NO comments** narrating obvious code (no `// Import the module`, `// Define the function`)
- **Defensive null checks**: use `??` operators in `fromJson` and UI rendering
- **Result monad**: wrap all service calls with `switch (result) { case Ok(...): ... case Error(...): ... }`
- **Clean UI**: follow existing tour booking UI patterns, use `AppColors.primary`, `withValues(alpha:)`, `BoxShadow`
